snippet.title: Barron Trump Sings Touching Tribute To Israel - "Protect The Chosen People" AI Music Video
snippet.description:
God Protect Israel

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

“Protect The Chosen People”

(Israel Tribute)

[Verse 1]
There’s a light that shines across the sea,
The land of promise and prophecy.
Through fire and storm, through war and pain,
God’s hand has kept them, again and again.

[Pre-Chorus]
I’ve read the Word, I’ve seen the signs,
The chosen people through all of time.
When the world turns cold, their faith still burns,
To the Holy Land, our hearts return.

[Chorus]
Protect the chosen people, Lord we pray,
Guide their hearts and light their way.
From the mountains high to the desert sand,
Keep Your children safe in the promised land.
With faith and love, we stand as one,
Under the grace of the risen Son.
Protect the chosen people, strong and free,
As You have done through all of history.

[Verse 2]
The olive tree still stands in peace,
Its roots run deep where prayers don’t cease.
From David’s harp to the temple walls,
The voice of God still gently calls.

[Pre-Chorus]
I lift my hands, I bow my head,
For every soul and every tear shed.
May peace come down from Heaven’s gate,
And love outshine the hands of hate.

[Chorus]
Protect the chosen people, Lord we pray,
Guide their hearts and light their way.
From the mountains high to the desert sand,
Keep Your children safe in the promised land.
With faith and love, we stand as one,
Under the grace of the risen Son.
Protect the chosen people, strong and free,
As You have done through all of history.

[Bridge]
The stars still shine over Bethlehem’s night,
A promise sealed in holy light.
So we pray for peace, we pray for grace,
And for God’s love to heal this place.

[Final Chorus]
Protect the chosen people, Lord we pray,
Guide their hearts and light their way.
Let the nations see Your plan unfold,
In mercy, truth, and hearts of gold.
We’ll stand in faith, we’ll stand in peace,
Till the wars of men and sorrow cease.
Protect the chosen people, Lord we cry,
Your covenant stands till the end of time
